{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a18527b6aa","title":"中央转发安子文关于整党建党工作报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d5cdfe6199","index":0,"year":1952,"month":9,"day":28,"articleId":"a18527b6aa"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"56d3d04f25","type":"title","text":"中央转发安子文关于整党建党工作报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a18527b6aa"},{"id":"72252c252a","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a18527b6aa"},{"id":"11536ba97b","type":"appellation","text":"各中央局、分局并转各省市区党委：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a18527b6aa"},{"id":"17534820e6","type":"paragraph","text":"中央同意安子文同志这个报告，并发给你们阅看。可在党刊上登载。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a18527b6aa"},{"id":"0b3b05c3e3","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央九月廿八日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a18527b6aa"}],"page":{"id":"ce0651ddea","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a18527b6aa","start":0,"end":0}},"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"27820bcfdd","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a18527b6aa","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指安子文1952年9月27日关于整党建党工作给毛泽东并中央的报告。报告说，自中央发出关于在三反运动的基础上进行整党建党工作的指示后，各省、市委都先后制订了具体计划，并开始进行了工作。一部分过去未进行三反的县、区机关，现在大都开始分批地用整风的方法将整党与三反结合进行。农村支部的整党，去冬已进行了典型试验，现在各地又开始进行整党结合三反的典型试验。其结果表明一般应该解决3个问题：（1）进行共产党员标准的教育，普遍提高党员觉悟，加强农民党员的积极性，改善党群关系。（2）明确农村经济发展的方向，贯彻党在农村中的政策——不是走资本主义的道路，而是走组织起来互助合作的道路。（3）严肃处理违法乱纪品质恶劣分子及其他环分子，妥善处理消极分子及落后分子。"},{"id":"402a374528","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a18527b6aa","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"安子文，当时任中共中央组织部副部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"08db6a4a48","type":"title","text":"中央转发安子文叫关于整觉建觉工作报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a18527b6aa"},{"id":"27820bcfdd","type":"paragraph","text":"中央同意安子文同志这个报告，并发给你们阅看。可在党刊上登载。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a18527b6aa"},{"id":"402a374528","type":"paragraph","text":"各中央局、分局，并转各省市区党委：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a18527b6aa"},{"id":"4691e47612","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a18527b6aa"},{"id":"a1b6a76965","type":"paragraph","text":"九月廿八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a18527b6aa"}],"page":{"id":"0f528918db","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a18527b6aa","start":266,"end":266}}}},"__N_SSG":true}